                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">This is the best I could come up with. The color makes no difference in speed at all. It's merely a status symbol.
<br />

<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Lizards</span>
<br />
Small Drum = Rope Bridle = 25% movement increase 
<br />

<br />
Drum = Leather Bridle = 50% movement increase 
<br />

<br />
Large Drum = Silken Bridle = 60% movement increase 
<br />

<br />
Giant Drum = Chain Bridle = 70% movement increase 
<br />

<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Horses</span>
<br />

<br />
Rope Bridle = 25% Movement Rate Increase (8000-13000PP) 
<br />

<br />
Leather Bridle = 50% Movement Rate Increase (27000-41000PP) 
<br />

<br />
Silken Bridle = 60% Movement Rate Increase (60000-85000PP) 
<br />

<br />
Chain Bridle = 70% Movement Rate Increase (95000-136000PP) 
<br />

<br />
Ornate Chain Bridle = 85% Movement Rate Increase (Only dropped off high level NPCs in Luclin) 
<br />

<br />
I'm not sure what the actual increase is with SOW or AA.. I'm sure someone does though</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><span style="text-decoration: underline">Quote of the Week:</span> 
