                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">JourneymanBoots: Increase Movement by 35%
<br />
Spirit of Wolf: Increase Movement by 34% (L9) to 55% (L50)
<br />
Spirt of Eagle:  Increase Movement by 57% (L54) to 60% (L60)
<br />
Selo's Accelerando:  Increase Movement by 20% (L5) to 65% (L50)
<br />
(I know this is more with a drum but I have no idea how that works)</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=317219" target="_blank" class="postlink">Mistress Regane Der'driu</a>
